    "title": {
      "rendered": "11 Holiday Gifts for Nonprofit Marketers &#038; Fundraisers"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p>&#8216;Tis the season to give! Nonprofit marketers and fundraisers spend all year focused on inspiring others to give and the holiday season is a good time to show your appreciation. The 11 gifts listed are less than $50 USD and curated to inspire fun and a little laughter.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2><strong>1) A Prayer for Grant Funding Candle</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>[$36] Sold by <a href=\"https://cognitive-surplus.com/collections/science-prayer-candles/products/a-prayer-for-grant-funding-cocktail-candle\">Cognitive Surplus</a>: </strong>Perfect for fundraisers and grant writers who have spent hours writing and re-writing grant proposals.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://cognitive-surplus.com/collections/science-prayer-candles/products/a-prayer-for-grant-funding-cocktail-candle\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42014 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Grant-Funding-Candle-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=626%2C588&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"626\" height=\"588\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Grant-Funding-Candle-for-Nonprofits.png?w=626&amp;ssl=1 626w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Grant-Funding-Candle-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=300%2C282&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Grant-Funding-Candle-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=50%2C47&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" /></a></p>\n<h2><strong>2) Greetings from Around the World Desk Calendar<br />\n</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>[$18] Sold by <a href=\"https://www.barnesandnoble.com/w/2025-greetings-from-around-the-world-desk-calendar-rifle-paper-co/1144629718\">Barnes &amp; Noble</a>: </strong>For the digital communication staff who work hard, but dream of travel and getting offline.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.barnesandnoble.com/w/2025-greetings-from-around-the-world-desk-calendar-rifle-paper-co/1144629718\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42017 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travel-Desk-Calendar-for-Nonprofit-Marketers.jpg?resize=600%2C610&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"610\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travel-Desk-Calendar-for-Nonprofit-Marketers.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travel-Desk-Calendar-for-Nonprofit-Marketers.jpg?resize=295%2C300&amp;ssl=1 295w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travel-Desk-Calendar-for-Nonprofit-Marketers.jpg?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travel-Desk-Calendar-for-Nonprofit-Marketers.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travel-Desk-Calendar-for-Nonprofit-Marketers.jpg?resize=80%2C80&amp;ssl=1 80w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2><strong>3) </strong>Ballpoint Pen</h2>\n<p><strong>[$40] Sold by <a href=\"https://www.ellingtonpens.com/products/ballpoint-pen-scarlet-slate\">Ellington Pens</a> and <a href=\"https://cross.com/collections/ballpoint-pen/products/at0112-18\">Cross</a>: </strong>Because who doesn&#8217;t love a good pen? Extra kudos for purchasing <a href=\"https://www.ellingtonpens.com/products/ballpoint-refills-copy\">refills</a>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.ellingtonpens.com/products/ballpoint-pen-scarlet-slate\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42020 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Ballpoint-pen-for-fundraisers.png?resize=526%2C507&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"526\" height=\"507\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Ballpoint-pen-for-fundraisers.png?w=526&amp;ssl=1 526w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Ballpoint-pen-for-fundraisers.png?resize=300%2C289&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Ballpoint-pen-for-fundraisers.png?resize=50%2C48&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 526px) 100vw, 526px\" /></a></p>\n<h2><strong>4) Notebook</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>[$19] Sold by <a href=\"https://wtfnotebooks.com/products/meetings-that-could-have-been-emails\">WTF/Notebooks</a>: </strong>Some of the best digital marketers and fundraisers still brainstorm ideas by hand.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://wtfnotebooks.com/products/meetings-that-could-have-been-emails\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42022 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Notebook-for-nonprofit-markerters.png?resize=620%2C627&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"620\" height=\"627\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Notebook-for-nonprofit-markerters.png?w=620&amp;ssl=1 620w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Notebook-for-nonprofit-markerters.png?resize=297%2C300&amp;ssl=1 297w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Notebook-for-nonprofit-markerters.png?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Notebook-for-nonprofit-markerters.png?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Notebook-for-nonprofit-markerters.png?resize=80%2C80&amp;ssl=1 80w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<h2><strong>5) Dashboard Spiral Deskpad</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>[$29] Sold by <a href=\"https://inkandvolt.com/products/ink-volt-dashboard-spiral-deskpad\">Ink+Volt</a>: </strong>For the social media managers that prefer old-school organization over Buffer or HootSuite. Bonus points for including <a href=\"https://www.pipsticks.com/products/out-of-office?_pos=2&amp;_sid=836e3cdc8&amp;_ss=r\">stickers</a>!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://inkandvolt.com/products/ink-volt-dashboard-spiral-deskpad\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-42026 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Organization-Pads-e1732720637356.png?resize=700%2C558&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"558\" /></a></p>\n<h2><strong>6) Reading Gift cards<br />\n</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>Sold by <a href=\"https://bookshop.org/gift_cards\">Bookshop.org</a>: </strong>Because book clubs and <a href=\"https://silentbook.club/\">reading in caf\u00e9s\u00a0and bars</a> are making a comeback!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://bookshop.org/p/books/empower-your-nonprofit-amy-neumann/21325911?ean=9781394263240\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42024 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/AI-Book-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=960%2C452&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"452\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/AI-Book-for-Nonprofits.png?w=981&amp;ssl=1 981w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/AI-Book-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=300%2C141&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/AI-Book-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=768%2C362&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/AI-Book-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=50%2C24&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" />[Buy Empower Your Nonprofit Book]</a></p>\n<h2>7) The Work Wellness Deck</h2>\n<p><strong>[$20] Sold by <a href=\"https://www.uncommongoods.com/product/the-work-wellness-deck/550620000000\">Uncommon Goods</a>: </strong><em>Burnout is real </em>and these cards are designed to REFRESH (mental health), FLOW (physical health), and CONNECT (work relationships).</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.uncommongoods.com/product/the-work-wellness-deck/550620000000\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-42036 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Work-Life-Balance-for-Nonprofits-e1732726351179.jpg?resize=575%2C714&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"575\" height=\"714\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Work-Life-Balance-for-Nonprofits-e1732726351179.jpg?w=575&amp;ssl=1 575w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Work-Life-Balance-for-Nonprofits-e1732726351179.jpg?resize=242%2C300&amp;ssl=1 242w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Work-Life-Balance-for-Nonprofits-e1732726351179.jpg?resize=40%2C50&amp;ssl=1 40w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<h2><strong>8) Business Card Case<br />\n</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>[$26] Sold by <a href=\"https://shop.mochithings.com/products/135294\">MochiThings</a> and <a href=\"https://www.leuchtturm1917.us/business-card-cases.html\">Leuchtturm1917</a>: </strong>Not all social networking and fundraising is online\u2014and conference season is coming!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://shop.mochithings.com/products/135294\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42047 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Fenice.jpg?resize=700%2C477&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"477\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Fenice.jpg?w=700&amp;ssl=1 700w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Fenice.jpg?resize=300%2C204&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Fenice.jpg?resize=50%2C34&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></p>\n<h2><strong>9) Cause Socks<br />\n</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>[$16-45] Sold by <a href=\"https://consciousstep.com/\">Conscious Step</a>: </strong>Put a little spring in their step with these fun and socially conscious socks.<a href=\"https://consciousstep.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42052 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Socks-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=800%2C666&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"666\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Socks-for-Nonprofits.png?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Socks-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=300%2C250&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Socks-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=768%2C639&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Socks-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=50%2C42&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></p>\n<h2><strong>10) Work from Anywhere Kit<br />\n</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>[$38] Sold by <a href=\"https://giftenmarket.com/products/work-from-anywhere-kit/\">Giften Market</a>: </strong>Hint, hint. <a href=\"https://www.deel.com/blog/workplace-statistics/\">Hybrid work schedules</a> are a win-win.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://giftenmarket.com/products/work-from-anywhere-kit/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42030 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/work-from-Anywhere-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=568%2C668&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"568\" height=\"668\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/work-from-Anywhere-for-Nonprofits.png?w=568&amp;ssl=1 568w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/work-from-Anywhere-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=255%2C300&amp;ssl=1 255w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/work-from-Anywhere-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=43%2C50&amp;ssl=1 43w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 568px) 100vw, 568px\" /></a></p>\n<h2><strong>11) Coffee Mug<br />\n</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>[$20] Sold by <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Marketer-Coffee-Mug-Profession-Marketing/dp/B08LDQMRCM\">Amazon</a>: </strong>Nonprofit marketers and fundraisers <em>are</em> always busy and they love coffee, as do the <a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/1708909513/social-media-manager-mug-personalised\">Social Media Queens &amp; Kings</a>!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/51oUONSGpqL._AC_SL1001_-e1732721463273.jpg?ssl=1\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42028 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/51oUONSGpqL._AC_SL1001_-e1732721463273.jpg?resize=500%2C509&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"509\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/certificate-programs/certificate-in-artificial-intelligence-ai-for-marketing-fundraising/\">2025 Certificate in Artificial Intelligence (AI) for Marketing &amp; Fundraising program</a> provides an honest, balanced approach to using AI for nonprofit marketing and fundraising\u2014and illuminates why human creativity is more valuable than ever. This certificate program will expand your skill set, advance your career, and help transition your nonprofit into the age of AI.</p>\n<p>The program requires the completion of three webinars and costs a total of $159 USD. To earn the certificate, you can attend the webinars live or view the recordings \u2013 or a combination of both. <a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/earn-a-certificate-in-digital-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/earn-a-certificate-in-social-media-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1653256738392000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1o7aYZXpgFGzJb7CozPKzZ\">Learn more &amp; register</a>!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/certificate-programs/certificate-in-artificial-intelligence-ai-for-marketing-fundraising/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-42727 size-full aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025-Certificate-in-AI-for-Nonprofits-e1739634358716.png?resize=900%2C707&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"707\" /></a></p>\n",
